  "title": "Mouthwatering Fluffy Middle Eastern Chicken Stir Fry",
  "description": "A fatty and fluffy Middle Eastern dish featuring oyster sauce, this stir fry is a crowd pleaser, kosher friendly and full of flavor. It combines the richness of chicken and spices with the savory taste of oyster sauce.",
