      "amount": "1/4 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "chopped parsley",
      "amount": "1/4 cup"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chicken to the skillet and cook until it is browned and cooked through.",
    "Add the cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Add the oyster sauce to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer the mixture for 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley.",
    "Serve the chicken and sauce over rice or with pita bread."
